{
  "page": "Elenda Baratheon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><div style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:distribute-all-lines\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caron\" title=\"House Caron\"><img alt=\"House Caron.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Caron.svg/40px-House_Caron.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"44\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Caron.svg/60px-House_Caron.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/House_Caron.svg/80px-House_Caron.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"44\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/60px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/80px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\"><img alt=\"House Connington.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/40px-House_Connington.svg.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"44\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/60px-House_Connington.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/80px-House_Connington.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display:inline-block;width:100%;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Elenda Baratheon</span></div></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Three_Widows_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Three Widows (The Rise of the Dragon).jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/Three_Widows_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/300px-Three_Widows_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/Three_Widows_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/450px-Three_Widows_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3c/Three_Widows_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/600px-Three_Widows_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Three widows, <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Lannister</a>, Elenda Baratheon, and <a href=\"/index.php/Samantha_Tarly\" title=\"Samantha Tarly\">Samantha Hightower</a> by Tomasz Jedruszek for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Lady Regent</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caron\" title=\"House Caron\">House Caron</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabt